Class FactoryStateMsg

  • java.lang.Object
    • FactoryStateMsg
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class FactoryStateMsg
extends Object
implements Serializable
    networking message containing all information needed to generate factory state note that if a client sends an empty FactoryStateMsg, it means they are requesting to be kept up-to-date with the factory state as long as it is connected to the server
    See Also:
